reviews.text:
The. Food was terribly overpriced.
They cheated us. Their lack of English knowledge killed me as they said something and did something else. The food was also atrocious, but that's all my opinion. It would be better if you went to the cooked food center opposite the street on the third floor.
Love the spicy chicken hotpot.  Price is reasonable.  Expect 300 per pax for dinner
Good service, good quality, tasteful, sceret place。
I was brought here by my friend who works in HK. This is her weekly Friday gathering place with her friends. Hotpot really delicious and there r exotic food items like pig's lungs and chicken balls.
